column5: My town was rated the best place to live in Canada. I'm sure that there's lots to be done to improve but I'm still glad that we're working on it.  http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/06/01/best-places-to-live-canada-moneysense_n_7486788.html?ncid=tweetlnkushpmg00000067
Very nice to see the place you live in is well rated.   Art
Roy, your living there probably gave it a boost in the ratings.
I've been meaning to visit for some time Roy.  Heard there's muskies up that way... and yourself too.  No wonder it's number one dood!
Certainly the best hospitality there is!
AWWWW shucks guys.....errr I mean gentlemen.
Heard today Barrie is #41, Up from  #120.
Well personally I have been there several times, and ya, it's okay
Didn't see much of it...it was dark when Roy picked us up at the Queen Elizabeth where we were celebrating our 25 th anny...  Yep...great hospitality at his place and paella....
